_content": "", "author": "rdvs34283", "created": 1775822002767, "profile_picture": "p9HQtdiLq2uP", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Liberats", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASZHmTXCI.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/WallStreetMav/status/2042353058957705419", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Gold has overtaken US Treasuries as the largest component of global central bank reserves for the first time since the mid-1990s.", "last_comment_created": 1775841720625, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 12, "score_up": 60, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"twitter": {"quotedTweet": false, "images": [{"width": 923, "heightRatio": 58, "url": "https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HFfiaPGXMAAogkz.jpg", "height": 537}], "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 65, "created": 1775769888000, "id": "2042353058957705419", "video": false, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1482179968083836928/7prxRZ4M_normal.jpg", "displayName": "Wall Street Mav", "username": "WallStreetMav"}, "content": "Gold has overtaken US Treasuries as the largest component of global central bank reserves for the first time since the mid-1990s.\n\nGold is rapidly replacing the US dollar as the global reserve currency.\n\nThe US dollar remains dominant in trade and finance. However, gold has", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 1455}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASZHmToFF", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 50, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8549201, "raw_content": "The Pleasures Found Only in Christ Jesus\n\n\u201cYou will show me the path of life: in your presence is fulness of joy; at your right hand there are pleasures for evermore.\u201d (Psalm 16:11)\n\nThe Path of Life: God reveals the way to live, leading to fulfillment, peace, and ultimately, eternal life. God reveals the law of the Spirit of Life in Christ that makes one free from the law of sin and death. Only in Christ is true joy -  not a fleeting emotion but a deep, complete satisfaction found in being with God.\n\nThese pleasures are not temporary, but are forevermore: The blessings of God are enduring, spiritual, and extend into eternity, symbolized by the \"right hand\" (a place of power and favor). The passage is often interpreted as a prophecy of Christ\u2019s resurrection and ascension, with Jesus now at the right hand of God, securing these pleasures for believers. \n\nWorship and Prayer: It is frequently used in prayers for guidance and to express confidence in God's presence in the midst of difficult circumstances. The verse serves as a reminder to focus on eternal hope, overcoming the fear of death by focusing on the promise of heaven. Many quote this scripture to emphasize that seeking God should be a daily priority. Abundant delight, complete satisfaction, total joy, lasting happiness.\n\nGod brings us into the law of the Spirit of life, with His indwelling guidance, and directing us into the righteous path He created us for. It is this communion with God, closeness, intimacy with God, that makes us free from the law of sin and death bringing us into the place of favor, authority, blessing, eternal delights, and everlasting joys.\n\nThe continual intercessory ministry of our Lord Jesus for His sheep is His main activity during this present age. Soon He will become God\u2019s strong right hand of power, manifested until all His enemies become His footstool and we, His people, are taken up to be with Him. Then we shall enjoy with Him the pleasures and fullness of joy at God\u2019s right hand forevermore.", "author": "Come-mistertallyman", "created": 1775825533639, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "HumphreyPlowjogger", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "The Pleasures Found Only in Christ Jesus", "last_comment_created": 1775830340214, "content": "<p>The Pleasures Found Only in Christ Jesus</p>\n<p>\u201cYou will show me the path of life: in your presence is fulness of joy; at your right hand there are pleasures for evermore.\u201d (Psalm 16:11)</p>\n<p>The Path of Life: God reveals the way to live, leading to fulfillment, peace, and ultimately, eternal life. God reveals the law of the Spirit of Life in Christ that makes one free from the law of sin and death. Only in Christ is true joy -  not a fleeting emotion but a deep, complete satisfaction found in being with God.</p>\n<p>These pleasures are not temporary, but are forevermore: The blessings of God are enduring, spiritual, and extend into eternity, symbolized by the &quot;right hand&quot; (a place of power and favor). The passage is often interpreted as a prophecy of Christ\u2019s resurrection and ascension, with Jesus now at the right hand of God, securing these pleasures for believers.</p>\n<p>Worship and Prayer: It is frequently used in prayers for guidance and to express confidence in God's presence in the midst of difficult circumstances. The verse serves as a reminder to focus on eternal hope, overcoming the fear of death by focusing on the promise of heaven. Many quote this scripture to emphasize that seeking God should be a daily priority. Abundant delight, complete satisfaction, total joy, lasting happiness.</p>\n<p>God brings us into the law of the Spirit of life, with His indwelling guidance, and directing us into the righteous path He created us for. It is this communion with God, closeness, intimacy with God, that makes us free from the law of sin and death bringing us into the place of favor, authority, blessing, eternal delights, and everlasting joys.</p>\n<p>The continual intercessory ministry of our Lord Jesus for His sheep is His main activity during this present age. Soon He will become God\u2019s strong right hand of power, manifested until all His enemies become His footstool and we, His people, are taken up to be with Him. Then we shall enjoy with Him the pleasures and fullness of joy at God\u2019s right hand forevermore.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 3, "score_up": 50, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2042298136580776229", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASZHlLQKD", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 464, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8548295, "raw_content": "", "author": "kinbergfan", "created": 1775781928828, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Underpants", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASZHlLQKD.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/C_3C_3/status/2042298136580776229", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Donald Trump continues to be the only President in history blocked from making recess appointmen